lass=m><span class=title> Re: The First Visit to the Great Hall</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Ravnanger trudges up the last few yards to the keep of Clan MacLear. It has been another arduous journey returning from the Frozen lands at the end of the  world. Looking up to the main gates he spies a young woman standing there. Her hair a frozen pile of snow and ice as the large flakes of snow descend from the grey sky. She turns as he approaches.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Failte Lass, what ye be doing standing out in the cold..and dressed poorly at that?&quot;  he says with a smile. Lanladori gives him a stoic look and informs him she waits to enter the hall.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Ravnanger looks at her for a moment. Trying to see a hint of her character. Being a shaman he has a way with the spirits of people and counts himself a good judge of character</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Well lass I can see yer strong enough to not have frozen to death out here. Come...inside it is warm and we can speak over dinner for I have not eaten a hot meal in days.'<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Ravnanger gives the word to the guards and they open the doors of the keep. Looking around he notices many more on duty then before. Turning he sees she hasn't moved. Smiling he beckons her to come</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Come lass I won't bite. I am known as Ravnanger...a shaman of MacLear...what be your name, and why might you have come to our halls?&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  They walk into the court yard and then the keep proper. Ravnanger makes a beeline to the kitchens where a scent of rabbit stew catches his nose, Lanaladori following behind.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/btheclanmaclear.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ravnanger>Ravnanger</A> at: 1/28/02 5:07:48 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ulanladori.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lanladori</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lad/Lass</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#330000>(1/28/02 5:33:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1368.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The First Visit to the Great Hall</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Purposefully following Ravnanger, Lanladori does not betray her surprise at meeting one of the MacLears so soon after her arrival.  She had expected to stand there all night in the cold.  Taking in her surroundings, she notices that the Great Hall is both aged and beautiful.<br>
<br>
Lanladori softly replies,</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> &quot;The one called Timo recruited me for a mission.  I need to provide my update in person.  You may call me Lanladori.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/btheclanmaclear.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ravnanger>Ravnanger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble</span><br>  Posts: 166<br> <font color=#330000>(1/28/02 5:47:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1368.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The First Visit to the Great Hall</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Ravnanger eyes the young girl as she speaks. Grabbing two bowls and spoons he ladles out some of the Rabbit stew that was left in the kettle to keep warm. He offers her a choice of mammoth milk, water or ale</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Pleased to meet you Lanladori. Timo may or may not be about, but your welcome to wait for him or to scribe a message to him in our great hall. I suggest after ye eat yer stew you go and see High Shamaness Lanadena. She may know where Timo is, or at least how to get in contact with him. But for now eat well to keep you warm. Ill see to it you get some warmer clothes...at least a woolen cloak.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ulanladori.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lanladori</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lass</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#330000>(1/28/02 6:26:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1368.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The First Visit to the Great Hall</span><hr size=1> &quot;I'll take the water, please.  You are very kind, but I have no need for a woolen cloak.  I don't believe my stay will be long enough to require one. &quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Ravnanger carries a tray with the bowls, drinks and spoons to a long table with many place settings.  He sets a place for the girl and a place for him.  Lanladori sits down at the place setting with the glass of water.  Ravnanger returns the tray to the kitchen area and returns to the dining area.  Ravnanger notices the fire in the hearth is low.  He sets more logs of wood upon it and stokes the hot coals before taking his seat next to Lanladori.  <br>
<br>
He raises the spoon to his lips and says, </i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;As you wish, Lass.&quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>   As the girl begins to eat her rabbit stew, he decides that she has not eaten in many days.  Lanladori gulps down some of her water with every few bites of stew.  She does not seem to notice that the heat of the fire is slowly turning her long hair into a wet mess on her shoulders.  Furthermore, he notices that her clothing looks like wet silk and is clinging to her body.   </i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/btheclanmaclear.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ravnanger>Ravnanger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble</span><br>  Posts: 169<br> <font color=#330000>(1/29/02 5:40:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1368.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The First Visit to the Great Hall</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Ravnanger watches the girl wolf down the rabbit stew. He pauses for a moment and then starts in on the stew himself. Between bites he speaks</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Suit yer self Lass. At least dry off a bit by the fire before you go outdoors again. With wet hair like that you'll certainly catch yer death out in the wilds. Everfrost is no place to be half naked and soaking wet when a storm rides through.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> He see that she has finished her bowl of stew. Rising he grabs the pot of stew, bringing it over to the table and filling her bowl again</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ulanladori.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lanladori</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lass</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#330000>(1/30/02 12:10:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1368.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The First Visit to the Great Hall</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Lanladori quietly thanks Ravnanger for the meal.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->  &quot;I'll be happy to help with the dishes, Ravnanger.  Or any other chores while I await Timo or the Lady Lanadena.  I'm not sure who knows of my mission, so it is probably best that I speak only with them to provide my report.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ulanladori.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lanladori</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mysterious Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#330000>(2/10/02 1:30:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1368.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The First Visit to the Great Hall</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Days Later</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Lanladori remains a quiet presence, waiting for acknowledgment from Timo or Lanadena. During the day she chops firewood and draws water from the well.  Sometimes she can be seen looking at the window, as though she were waiting for a friend to arrive.  At night, she sleeps in a hardback chair in the Great Hall.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/umatach.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Matach</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lad</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#330000>(2/10/02 2:16:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1368.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The First Visit to the Great Hall</span><hr size=1>  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Shivering the whole way, Matach slowly makes his way through the ankle high snow. Grumbling to himself on why he picked a family that lived in this Ro forsaken place.. and why anyone would want to live here, he pulled his robe tighter against him. Looking up through the falling snow, which seemed to be falling harder and harder with each passing moment he eyed the entrance to the guild hall.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
 &quot;FINALLY! And I thought I would wander around this damned tundra forever.&quot;<br>
<br>
 <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Slowly pushing open the doors and walking by the guards, Matach stumbled inside, stamping his feet, half in frustration and half in trying to get the caked snow off his feet and bottom of his robe. Talking to no one in particular he yelled out.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
 &quot;I DO HOPE there is a HOT FIRE going! I am FREEZING!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ulanladori.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lanladori</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mysterious Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#330000>(2/10/02 4:28:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1368.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The First Visit to the Great Hall</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Awakened from her slumber, Lanladori slowly opens one eye.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
&quot;If there isn't a fire in the room you are headed to, the wood is here beside my chair.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=1368.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=1368.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1368.topic&index=9><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=1368.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.threadControl?topicID=1368.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1368.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1368.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub5.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="theclanmacleargeneral">The Great Hall<option value="theclanmaclearfrm8">Inner Court<option value="theclanmaclearfrm6">Events<option value="theclanmaclearfrm5">Provisioner's S